{"tid":2167148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「國安法保釋違無罪推定」 被告申人身保護令今裁決","createTime":"2020-08-21T01:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T02:35:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fa72295b1a6c19a6939f20c7fee8380a98641c5c","tid":2167148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T01:46:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/OEWTBR4YCZAXZD72AWRE5O3TZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FOEWTBR4YCZAXZD72AWRE5O3TZU%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuyBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=81e3875d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FOEWTBR4YCZAXZD72AWRE5O3TZU%2F&h=ee160589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/OEWTBR4YCZAXZD72AWRE5O3TZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「國安法保釋違無罪推定」<br />\n被告申人身保護令今裁決<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eQYmrmZXMp0GeaHXhLbRV8Iv1FI=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BOGVGUCLZFGK7NXBJIZLYRWIPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeQYmrmZXMp0GeaHXhLbRV8Iv1FI%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBOGVGUCLZFGK7NXBJIZLYRWIPI.jpg&h=7e7c19f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■國安法首位被告唐英傑早前申請保釋被拒繼續還柙。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【法庭直擊】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】首名被控違反港區國安法煽動他人分裂國家等罪的被告，早前被裁判官拒絕保釋後，向高院申請人身保護令，若成功可即時獲釋候訊。案件昨開審，申請方指國安法的保釋要求有違無罪推定，變相要被告承認做過危害國家安全行為，而控方毋須提供反對保釋理據，會增加任意逮捕風險。政府指國安法凌駕本地法律，香港法院無解釋權。法官今午裁決。<br />\n<br />\n申請人唐英傑（23歲）由資深大律師戴啟思、大律師黃瑞紅等代表；資深大狀余若海等人代表政府答辯。案件由周家明及李運騰審理，兩人皆是特首林鄭月娥欽點的指定法官。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n須承諾不「繼續」危害國安<br />\n<br />\n黃瑞紅陳詞指，國安法被告若要保釋，須說服法官同意他「不會繼續實施」危害國安行為，而《辭淵》定義。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n戴啟思則指，任何在香港生效的法律，必須有真實和經核證的英文版本，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n余若海反駁指，申請人不是遭非法拘押，合法羈押下繼續扣押並不違反人身保護令要求，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n戴啟思回應指，國安法第4條寫明人權應受保障，而保釋是人們其中一項權利，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n昨在庭外觀看聆訊直播的一名劉姓女子，以手提電話拍攝直播畫面，被法官傳召問話，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCAL1601/20"},{"pid":"c6c80c0b3f11fcdc7dc4621ffe8e2778449824d3","tid":2167148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"大家要定時定候捐款去 612基金，長期作戰嚟。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fMfMbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fMfMbS</a>"},{"pid":"8cb4118969da2536faa9de4b697028d28d36b854","tid":2167148,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T01:48:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb639cddd9018ded7176a16ef0fe6c190609d8bc","tid":2167148,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T01:58:22.000Z","msg":"蘋果入面張圖都好笑 咩雙方理據, 而家擺明獨裁<br />\n你會唔會好認真去咁研究大清律例呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《大清律》源自《大明律》，比《大明律》刑罰更重，清朝對於謀反大逆處斬的範圍與明代相當，<span class=\"red\">但擴大了謀反罪的範圍，例如奏疏不當或犯聖違逆者，加以「殊屬喪心病狂」、「妄議朝政」之罪以謀反罪論。</span>"},{"pid":"8a17a8a9b260dc57a518dd4c6229b557bff615a3","tid":2167148,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T01:59:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ab0b5d418fcc77ac0f74e1d026ee73dbcea201a","tid":2167148,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791b935513be15dcdae3b054453b3004195046be","tid":2167148,"uid":272371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:12:39.000Z","msg":"法律上無罪，政治上有罪"},{"pid":"a3139e66a63d48ac4bb5d64cbe485120d40edcce","tid":2167148,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:32:55.000Z","msg":"推"